age failures and handoff breakage. REAL-INFRA: yes (real upload/network/external services). LLM-DEP: yes (real STT/LLM outputs required). MULTI-STEP: yes, multiple agentic steps in sequence across full pipeline. INTEGRATION-BRAKE: (a) yes real infra, (b) yes real AI output, (c) yes chained agentic stages => Workflow is required. Rejection gate: System and Agentic rejected because behavior text explicitly requires the full multi-stage pipeline, not just one external call or one model step.","test_description":"Execute an end-to-end run on a real meeting audio file in a production-like environment: upload, transcribe via real STT, summarize via real LLM, and deliver structured output; assert no manual intervention, successful completion, and valid final structured payload.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.0,"Integration":0.03,"System":0.07,"Agentic":0.15,"Workflow":0.75}}]}
